name: Ibtissam Tiskat
description: '''Ibtissam Tiskat''' ({{langx|ar|إبتسام تسكت}}; born 3 October 1992) is a Moroccan singer and actress who rose to popularity as a contestant in both the second season of ''[[Arab Idol]]'' and the tenth season of ''[[Star Academy Arab World]]''. She made her commercial singing debut with "N'dir Mabghit" ({{langx|ar|ندير ما بغيت}}) in September 2014.
